data.title: Deron Williams, Basketball Player
data.meta_description: Deron Williams stats and bio. Stats averages season by season. Quick access to game by game stats.
data.text:
Deron Williams - Points

Deron Williams scores a career high 57 points (2012)

On March 04, 2012, Deron Williams set his career high in points in a NBA game. That day he scored 57 points in New Jersey's road win against Charlotte, 101-104. He also had 6 rebounds, 7 assists, 1 steal and 1 block. He shot 12/18 from two, 4/11 from three, shooting at 55.2% from the field. He also shot 21/21 from the free-throw line.

Deron Williams - Rebounds

Deron Williams grabs a career high 9 rebounds (2010)

On February 10, 2010, Deron Williams tied his career high in rebounds in a NBA game. That day he grabbed 9 rebounds in Utah's home loss against LA Lakers, 81-96. He also had 11 points, 10 assists, 3 steals.

Deron Williams - Assists

Deron Williams gives a career high 21 assists (2007)

On January 24, 2007, Deron Williams tied his career high in assists in a NBA game. That day he dished 21 assists in Utah's home loss against Memphis, 130-132. He also had 7 points, 5 rebounds and 1 block.

Deron Williams - Steals

Deron Williams has a career high 6 steals (2014)

On February 23, 2014, Deron Williams set his career high in steals in a NBA game. That day he reached 6 steals in Brooklyn's road win against LA Lakers, 102-108. He also had 30 points, 5 rebounds and 7 assists.

Deron Williams - Blocks

Deron Williams blocks a career high 4 shots (2012)

On November 25, 2012, Deron Williams set his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Brooklyn's home win against Portland, 98-85. He also had 15 points, 2 rebounds and 12 assists.

Deron Williams - Efficiency

Deron Williams records a career high 54 efficiency rating (2012)

On March 04, 2012, Deron Williams set his career high in efficiency in a NBA game. That day he accomplished 54 efficiency in New Jersey's road win against Charlotte, 101-104. He also had 57 points, 6 rebounds and 7 assists.
